title: My 10 Books - October 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 books, all in ePUB format. Covers included in separate folder:

01. Accidental Saints - Finding God in All the Wrong People
02. Alien Universe - Extraterrestrial Life in Our Minds and in the Cosmos
03. Astrosex - Sexual Secrets Revealed through the Stars
04. DIY Bedroom Decor - 50 Awesome Ideas for Your Room
05. Hunting and Imaging Comets by Martin Mobberley
06. McGraw-Hill's Math, Grade 7
07. Puzzling Adventures - Tales of Strategy, Logic, and Mathematical Skill
08. The Cambridge Textbook of Bioethics by Singer & Viens
09. Windows 10 Revealed - The Universal Windows Operating System for PC, Tablets, and Windows Phone
10. The Lost World of Byzantium by Jonathan Harris
